metadata.name: Checks Invaders #1
metadata.description: 'Checks Invaders' is a crossover project combining the popular art project 'Checks' by Jack Butcher and the iconic retro game 'Space Invaders.' The project brings together the colorful and minimalistic aesthetic of 'Checks' with the 8-bit pixelated style of 'Space Invaders' to create a unique and visually striking piece of art.
